{"tid":945696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港客遊台小心！大陸新娘帶15塊豬肉乾 被罰$5萬","createTime":"2018-12-18T05:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T05:50:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15c590611e366fe7c680c8c15036aabf8eb618f2","tid":945696,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181218/large/1545110246_245e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181218%2Flarge%2F1545110246_245e.jpg&h=531ef5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人遊台，千萬不要攜帶肉類製品到當地！非洲豬瘟疫情持續在中國爆發，台灣為防範疫情傳入，今日起加強處罰違規攜帶肉類製品入境的旅客。今早11時許，一名從大陸嫁到台灣的何姓女子，從福州搭機抵達桃園機場，遭當地海關及防檢局人員截查，被發現攜帶15片豬肉乾。台海關隨即開出桃園機場自提高罰款後首張20萬元新台幣（下同、約5萬港元）的罰單。<br />\n<br />\n何姓女子向海關表示，在大陸買15片豬肉乾花了20多元人民幣（22.6港元），總重約200公克，強調並不知道不能帶肉類入境台灣。防檢局人員出示公文，告知她一直以來都禁止帶肉類入境，現在為了防範非洲豬瘟入境台灣，才提高罰款。為顧及20萬元罰款金額過高，防檢局人員特別提醒何女，如要分期付款繳納，需要事先提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣所修定的法例，任何旅客自最近3年發生非洲豬瘟的國家或地區攜帶肉類製品入境，均屬違法，初犯罰款20萬元，第二次起罰100萬元（25.36萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181218/59042970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59042970&d=80JSO3C4DhQkSCqIxZi%2BVwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=19a3e335\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59042970&h=e1dbb586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181218/59042970</a>"},{"pid":"fa62ed43d12bafcbe4cb76ed16ef7896e6a44e59","tid":945696,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"連仔：香港好撚守法的，蘋果垃圾標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c616d18f9d5f99d625d047e4c770d538ccc1e","tid":945696,"uid":64601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa62ed43d12bafcbe4cb76ed16ef7896e6a44e59","tid":945696,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"連仔：香港好撚守法的，蘋果垃圾標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"要抽水就用下腦啦"}]}